ign sense and an eye for simple and  elegant user interfaces Deep understanding of iOS UX and UI design  paradigmsFamiliarity and experience with Agile (scrum) development process  Understanding of data modeling and design patterns.Experience with iOS UI  prototyping best practices and knowledge working with Interface builderPointers  SWIFT/Objective C Programming Programming fundamentals in Swift/Objective C  Swift/Objective C Standard Library Reference- Classes, Structures,  Enumerations, Protocols, Functions/closures, Operators, type aliases Unit  testing with SWIFT / Objective C- Mocking Objects, Behavior Driven Development  ( Quick and Nimble tools)Handling Objective C in SWIFT and SWIFT in Objective C  Handling external Libraries in SWIFT / Objective C Specific in Swift /  Objective C- Vector based UI / Scalable UI / Adaptable UI / Auto layout  Specific in Swift / Objective C- Multi thread programmingSpecific in Swift /  Objective C- App security obfuscation of code, API level security, Handling 3rd  Party interfaces/libraries Specific in Swift / Objective C- Parallel  programming especially GPU core for faster UI renderingSpecific in Swift /  Objective C- Understanding and Handling connectivity Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, VPN and  data networkcode-coverage tool configuration and debugging- both when Swift is  used inside Objective C and Objective C used inside Swift iOS specifics  Programming- Fragment Management, Activity lifecycle, Security, profiling,  material design, Performance Tuning and Optimizing iOS Application','/video/company_image/c60ab65d-b986-4859-9d80-6ab7a67cc17b.jpg', now(), now());
insert into organization (id, name, org_type, address_id, industry, profile, image, created_at, updated_at) values (101,'Mindteck','COMPANY',2784,'IT & ITES','Mindteck, a global technology company established in 1991, provides Product  Engineering solutions and Information Technology services to top-tier Fortune  100 companies, start-ups, leading universities and government entities. Its  depth of knowledge and niche expertise in embedded systems and enterprise  applications is complemented by dedicated Centers of Excellence in wireless  design and storage testing. The company has offices in the US, UK, Singapore,  Malaysia, Netherlands, Germany, Bahrain and India. It also has four development  centers: one each in the US and Singapore, and two in India (Kolkata and  Bangalore). Mindteck is listed on the Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE 517344) and is  among a select group of global companies appraised at Maturity Level 5, Version  1.3 of the CMMI Institute?s Capability Maturity Model Integration (CMMI).','/video/company_image/0ef82665-8126-4670-833e-f65332136514.jpg', now(), now());
insert into organization (id, name, org_type, address_id, industry, profile, image, created_at, updated_at) values (149,'Tata ELXSI Ltd','COMPANY',2833,'IT & ITES','Tata Elxsi is a design company that blends technology, creativity and engineering to help customers transform ideas into world-class products and solutions. A part of the $100 billion+ Tata group, Tata Elxsi addresses the communications, consumer products, defence, healthcare, media &amp; entertainment, semiconductor and transportation sectors. This is supported by a network of design studios, development centers and offices worldwide. Tata Elxsi is a listed company and headquartered in Bangalore, India. 											 											','/video/company_image/3f16dcb5-6530-47fc-baa3-ee09a5a52f37.jpg', now(), now());
